["Sand Springs is an unincorporated community and census-designated place in Howard County, Texas, United States. Its population was 835 as of the 2010 census.[1] Interstate 20 passes through the community.","According to the U.S. Census Bureau, the community has an area of 2.570 square miles (6.66\u00a0km2), all of it land.[1]","This article about a location in Howard County, Texas is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it."]